1
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa! This one!</font>

2
00:00:26,220 --> 00:00:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see. Ah, <i>Yun Yun the 
Servant and Pudding the Witch</i>.</font>

3
00:00:31,460 --> 00:00:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really do love this book, don't you?</font>

4
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup!</font>

5
00:00:35,730 --> 00:00:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno why, but when 
you read me this book,</font>

6
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can sleep real good!</font>

7
00:00:45,330 --> 00:00:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's good.</font>

8
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, Papa will read it for 
you, so make sure you sleep soundly.</font>

9
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

10
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty!</font>

11
00:00:55,130 --> 00:00:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you shirking your 
duties and putting Lady Doux to bed?</font>

12
00:00:58,430 --> 00:01:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still noon! Noon!</font>

13
00:01:01,230 --> 00:01:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be such a spoilsport.</font>

14
00:01:03,010 --> 00:01:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no harm in coming to see 
Doux during her nap time, is there?</font>

15
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is! You still have 
a mountain of work to do!</font>

16
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Doux.</font>

17
00:01:19,930 --> 00:01:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sound...</font>

18
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux!</font>

19
00:01:28,930 --> 00:01:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

20
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I've missed you so, Doux!</font>

21
00:01:34,310 --> 00:01:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look how big you've gotten!</font>

22
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-Wh-What is the meaning of this?!</font>

23
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm Jahi!</font>

24
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

25
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! So you've returned from 
your world conquest, Dahaka!</font>

26
00:01:48,860 --> 00:01:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darling!</font>

27
00:01:53,710 --> 00:01:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is the great Azi Dahaka?</font>

28
00:01:59,930 --> 00:02:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dragon of calamity who can bring about</font>

29
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">catastrophes powerful enough to
 destroy gods that is</font>

30
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">conquering the world by herself.</font>

31
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she's Lady Doux's...</font>

32
00:02:11,730 --> 00:02:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">mother?!</font>

33
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE DEMON KING'S WIFE LOVES
HER DAUGHTER TOO MUCH!!</font>

34
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The Demon King's Wife Loves 
Her Daughter Too Much!!"</i></font>

35
00:03:53,890 --> 00:03:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dahaka...</font>

36
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How goes world domination?</font>

37
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it didn't work out.</font>

38
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though we were apart, my heart 
as a mother grew even fonder...</font>

39
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I even ended up feeling 
love for a human child.</font>

40
00:04:09,060 --> 00:04:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no time for conquering anything!</font>

41
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! I know exactly how that feels!</font>

42
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, so they're both doting parents.</font>

43
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux?</font>

44
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux! There you are!</font>

45
00:04:27,230 --> 00:04:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home! Come here! It's your mama!</font>

46
00:04:33,610 --> 00:04:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello...</font>

47
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-D-D-Doux?</font>

48
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-Why are you acting 
like we've never met before?</font>

49
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I feared this would happen.</font>

50
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, Your Majesty?</font>

51
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux doesn't remember Dahaka.</font>

52
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was inevitable.</font>

53
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dahaka left to conquer the world before 
Doux was old enough to remember.</font>

54
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is that?!</font>

55
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:06,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is bad! That's 
Dahaka's power at work.</font>

56
00:05:06,890 --> 00:05:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Depending on Dahaka's mood, she can bring 
about all kinds of great disasters!</font>

57
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

58
00:05:14,130 --> 00:05:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is there suddenly a storm?!</font>

59
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run away!</font>

60
00:05:21,250 --> 00:05:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's all right, Lady Dahaka!</font>

61
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure Lady Doux will 
remember you very soon.</font>

62
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jahi is right.</font>

63
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I know!</font>

64
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you play with 
Doux like you used to?</font>

65
00:05:37,020 --> 00:05:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That might help her remember.</font>

66
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's a brilliant idea! 
Now, let's go, Lady Dahaka!</font>

67
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right!</font>

68
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's sure to remember 
me if we play together.</font>

69
00:05:54,570 --> 00:05:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was close...</font>

70
00:05:58,290 --> 00:06:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it appears that Doux is unsure 
how to interact with her mother.</font>

71
00:06:04,170 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope she is able to remember 
something as they're playing.</font>

72
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This takes me back.</font>

73
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We used to walk on the beach like this.</font>

74
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember, Doux?</font>

75
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh.</font>

76
00:06:19,130 --> 00:06:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see...</font>

77
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear...</font>

78
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dahaka! Perhaps she'll remember 
if you two have a little race.</font>

79
00:06:29,030 --> 00:06:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Of course.</font>

80
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess Doux is able 
to walk by herself now.</font>

81
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:39,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Let's race to those rocks!</font>

82
00:06:46,890 --> 00:06:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had forgotten.</font>

83
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She...</font>

84
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has absolutely no idea how to hold back.</font>

85
00:06:59,810 --> 00:07:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made a lot, so eat up!</font>

86
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used to love these sweets,
 so I made them for you all the time.</font>

87
00:07:09,570 --> 00:07:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember?</font>

88
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

89
00:07:15,370 --> 00:07:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they're really yummy.</font>

90
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

91
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said that she would like 
to be alone for a while.</font>

92
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

93
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure that it was quite a shock 
that Doux didn't remember anything.</font>

94
00:07:38,770 --> 00:07:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or rather, perhaps it's 
regret rather than shock.</font>

95
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What do you mean?</font>

96
00:07:51,890 --> 00:07:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before, Dahaka was a single 
dragon bent on world domination.</font>

97
00:07:58,660 --> 00:08:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she had an evil side that 
wanted to take over the world</font>

98
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a gentle side that brought 
blessings and healing to the world.</font>

99
00:08:09,770 --> 00:08:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And since I needed the 
powers of her evil side,</font>

100
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used a bracelet called the 
Heavenly Ring of Evil...</font>

101
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and split her into two beings, 
one evil and one good.</font>

102
00:08:26,130 --> 00:08:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they are... Doux and Dahaka.</font>

103
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

104
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Y-Y-You never told me that before!</font>

105
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you're surprised.</font>

106
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that means neither of 
us are technically her parents.</font>

107
00:08:39,350 --> 00:08:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

108
00:08:42,170 --> 00:08:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thank you, Ahriman.</font>

109
00:08:44,710 --> 00:08:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I can concentrate on taking over 
the world without any distractions.</font>

110
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right...</font>

111
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:56,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no need for a good heart!</font>

112
00:09:07,190 --> 00:09:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama!</font>

113
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa!</font>

114
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

115
00:09:16,590 --> 00:09:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was Doux's first words 
that made us family.</font>

116
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I had no idea that Lady 
Doux had such a secret.</font>

117
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so, I decided to raise 
Doux into a proper demon.</font>

118
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Dahaka believed that</font>

119
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">her love for Doux would get in the way 
of her ambition for world domination,</font>

120
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so she left on a journey 
alone to take over the world.</font>

121
00:09:44,130 --> 00:09:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm certain that she 
regrets that decision.</font>

122
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, where is Lady Doux?</font>

123
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux...</font>

124
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

125
00:10:26,270 --> 00:10:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine. I was just having 
some trouble sleeping.</font>

126
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then Doux will read this for you!</font>

127
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

128
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought a picture book!</font>

129
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I read this, you'll calm down.</font>

130
00:10:40,770 --> 00:10:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see...</font>

131
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Once upon a time, there 
was a servamp named Yun Yun</font>

132
00:10:48,230 --> 00:10:53,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a m-musician? Named Pudding.</font>

133
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pudding always"... Um...</font>

134
00:10:57,030 --> 00:11:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see it. I'll read it with you.</font>

135
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

136
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see...</font>

137
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Once upon a time, there 
was a servant named Yun Yun</font>

138
00:11:06,950 --> 00:11:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a magician named Pudding.</font>

139
00:11:09,890 --> 00:11:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pudding always did bad things, 
and Yun Yun was always crying.</font>

140
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how they were, they didn't 
actually dislike each other.</font>

141
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then one day..."</font>

142
00:11:28,490 --> 00:11:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This book...</font>

143
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So when Papa reads me this picture book,</font>

144
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even after I fall asleep, someone 
reads it in my dreams, too.</font>

145
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't remember who that was...</font>

146
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but now I remember!</font>

147
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes... Right.</font>

148
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, how about I read the 
rest of the book for you then?</font>

149
00:11:55,250 --> 00:12:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}"LET'S READ THE PICTURE BOOK"
LYRICS: KANATA NAKAMURA
 COMPOSITION AND ARRANGEMENT: NAOKI YANAGISAWA
SONG: DOUX</font>

150
00:11:57,740 --> 00:11:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

151
00:11:59,230 --> 00:12:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, go change into your pajamas.</font>

152
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

153
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}There's someone just 
beyond my fluffy dreams</i></font>

154
00:12:09,430 --> 00:12:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I wonder who it is</i></font>

155
00:12:14,190 --> 00:12:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They have a really, really kind voice</i></font>

156
00:12:18,940 --> 00:12:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As they speak to me</i></font>

157
00:12:24,110 --> 00:12:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Only my fuzzy memories came to me before</i></font>

158
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But now, I think I remember</i></font>

159
00:12:43,050 --> 00:12:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Mama, Mama</i></font>

160
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That word fills me with joy</i></font>

161
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Mama, Mama</i></font>

162
00:12:57,230 --> 00:13:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I want to call to her even more</i></font>

163
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"And so, Pudding the Witch 
disappeared into the night sky.</font>

164
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The end."</font>

165
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

166
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back, Mama!</font>

167
00:13:15,690 --> 00:13:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home now, Doux.</font>

168
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE FACE REVEAL CEREMONY IS TOO SOON!!</font>

169
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The Face Reveal Ceremony Is Too Soon!!"</i></font>

170
00:13:26,850 --> 00:13:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Face Reveal Ceremony.</i></font>

171
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A ceremony carried out by 
demons since time immemorial.</i></font>

172
00:13:32,290 --> 00:13:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is a tradition where the demon 
king's heir reveals their face</i></font>

173
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to all in the demon castle 
when they are still young.</i></font>

174
00:13:40,210 --> 00:13:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Doux was about to undergo this ceremony.</i></font>

175
00:13:44,710 --> 00:13:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going now!</font>

176
00:13:46,980 --> 00:13:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you come back for lunch!</font>

177
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

178
00:13:54,390 --> 00:13:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Dahaka!</font>

179
00:13:57,720 --> 00:14:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Have you seen Lady Doux?</font>

180
00:14:00,410 --> 00:14:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking everywhere for her!</font>

181
00:14:02,690 --> 00:14:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux just left for a walk just now.</font>

182
00:14:05,740 --> 00:14:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A walk? But she has no time for that!</font>

183
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Face Reveal Ceremony is soon!</font>

184
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need Lady Doux to properly act 
like the demon king's daughter</font>

185
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and to memorize her lines immediately!</font>

186
00:14:18,740 --> 00:14:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dahaka!</font>

187
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:23,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so worried!</font>

188
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will Doux actually be able to 
stand in front of a huge crowd</font>

189
00:14:26,410 --> 00:14:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and properly say her lines?</font>

190
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps we should just do this 
in front of the ones we know.</font>

191
00:14:31,970 --> 00:14:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty!</font>

192
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, Lady Doux 
needs to do her dress rehearsal!</font>

193
00:14:36,540 --> 00:14:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, "More importantly"?! 
What if this traumatizes her?!</font>

194
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go babying her again!
Your Majesty, this is all because...</font>

195
00:14:45,310 --> 00:14:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, you're far 
too strict with Doux!</font>

196
00:14:48,370 --> 00:14:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down, both of you.</font>

197
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, ma'am.</font>

198
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly...</font>

199
00:14:56,820 --> 00:15:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you two, who are the closest to her, 
don't believe in her, then who will?</font>

200
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

201
00:15:03,290 --> 00:15:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're that worried, then 
go find Doux right now.</font>

202
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll know immediately that 
there's no need to worry.</font>

203
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find Lady Doux?</font>

204
00:15:12,850 --> 00:15:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Granny! I got lots of big cormbs!</font>

205
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:20,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, those are fine corn cobs.</font>

206
00:15:20,650 --> 00:15:23,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why don't we let you take those?</font>

207
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

208
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you're always helping me out.</font>

209
00:15:28,850 --> 00:15:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me at least do this for you.</font>

210
00:15:30,860 --> 00:15:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

211
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux...</font>

212
00:15:36,620 --> 00:15:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We came here as Lady Dahaka insisted,
and Lady Doux is already helping a human!</font>

213
00:15:44,260 --> 00:15:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea Doux came to 
a village so far away again.</font>

214
00:15:47,950 --> 00:15:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you impressed?</font>

215
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot agree with Lady Dahaka.</font>

216
00:15:53,690 --> 00:15:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are far too many things 
to do before the ceremony.</font>

217
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no time for this! Wha—</font>

218
00:15:59,180 --> 00:16:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, wait, Jahi!</font>

219
00:16:01,010 --> 00:16:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's watch for a little while 
longer before we decide.</font>

220
00:16:07,610 --> 00:16:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one has the present?</font>

221
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

222
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The right one!</font>

223
00:16:13,610 --> 00:16:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Mayu! Doux gets to go first.</font>

224
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up! I'm gonna beat Doux this time!</font>

225
00:16:19,830 --> 00:16:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez...</font>

226
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux picks this one.</font>

227
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm...</font>

228
00:16:24,850 --> 00:16:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then Doux is our winner!</font>

229
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

230
00:16:27,380 --> 00:16:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Chocolate!</font>

231
00:16:30,050 --> 00:16:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You cheated just now, didn't you?</font>

232
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Santa only rewards the good kids.</font>

233
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it! You'll pay for this!</font>

234
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Here.</font>

235
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:45,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wha...</font>

236
00:16:45,770 --> 00:16:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't seem too disappointed. 
You must be in the spring of your youth.</font>

237
00:16:49,310 --> 00:16:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

238
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. He skipped out on his 
angel duties to come see Doux.</font>

239
00:16:55,060 --> 00:16:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shut up! You two are in the same boat!</font>

240
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're on break.</font>

241
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not Santa season right now.</font>

242
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't lump us in with you.</font>

243
00:17:05,290 --> 00:17:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, shut up, shut up!</font>

244
00:17:08,290 --> 00:17:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That halo... He couldn't be.</font>

245
00:17:08,290 --> 00:17:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Stupid! Stupid!</font>

246
00:17:10,170 --> 00:17:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, did she just say "Santa"?</font>

247
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Who does that greenhorn think he is?!</font>

248
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare he share some 
chocolate with Doux?!</font>

249
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please calm down, Your Majesty.</font>

250
00:17:25,490 --> 00:17:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! There's barely any 
ingredients in here!</font>

251
00:17:29,710 --> 00:17:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's not enough milk or seafood at all!</font>

252
00:17:32,540 --> 00:17:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When are we supposed to get more?</font>

253
00:17:34,990 --> 00:17:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, Chef...</font>

254
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're having some trouble 
with our vendor...</font>

255
00:17:39,490 --> 00:17:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! You can't be serious!</font>

256
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm putting my life on the line cooking!</font>

257
00:17:45,450 --> 00:17:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, what am I supposed to do? 
This isn't going to do at all...</font>

258
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:51,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master.</font>

259
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

260
00:17:52,540 --> 00:17:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

261
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux? This is for me?</font>

262
00:17:56,550 --> 00:18:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup! I heard you this morning 
saying there wasn't any food.</font>

263
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cormbs from Granny's fields 
are super sweet and yummy.</font>

264
00:18:08,770 --> 00:18:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll go with anything!</font>

265
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux...</font>

266
00:18:12,860 --> 00:18:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux!</font>

267
00:18:14,860 --> 00:18:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But, Chef! None of your 
recipes today need corn...</font>

268
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about that!</font>

269
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to Doux, I thought 
up an even better dish!</font>

270
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess Lady Doux helped Thaiti out.</font>

271
00:18:29,130 --> 00:18:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's grown into such a kind child.</font>

272
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, everyone! You don't 
need to rush so much!</font>

273
00:18:36,690 --> 00:18:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-What is this?!</font>

274
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? It's super good!</font>

275
00:18:42,940 --> 00:18:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never eaten something so delicious!</font>

276
00:18:45,930 --> 00:18:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But why do we slaves get some, too?</font>

277
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's enough for everyone! Here, Doux.</font>

278
00:18:56,430 --> 00:18:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

279
00:18:59,450 --> 00:19:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

280
00:19:01,950 --> 00:19:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, Doux is serving them food.</font>

281
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Unbelievable!</font>

282
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to eat food that 
Doux serves me, too.</font>

283
00:19:10,130 --> 00:19:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, stop being jealous and 
stop her, Your Majesty!</font>

284
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

285
00:19:17,410 --> 00:19:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came in time for the Face 
Reveal Ceremony and...</font>

286
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the dunce serving 
these lesser humans food?</font>

287
00:19:26,260 --> 00:19:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was I supposed to do?</font>

288
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Pawpaw!</font>

289
00:19:28,170 --> 00:19:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux said she wanted to eat with everyone.</font>

290
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence!</font>

291
00:19:32,980 --> 00:19:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your failure that you let 
her words sway your judgment.</font>

292
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop her at once.</font>

293
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or else...</font>

294
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will turn everyone involved 
into slabs of meat right now.</font>

295
00:19:46,990 --> 00:19:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>S-So this is the aura of
the previous demon king Zareth,</i></font>

296
00:19:50,270 --> 00:19:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>said to make even demons tremble...</i></font>

297
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Brilliant! I'm sure that Lord Zareth 
will be able to stop Lady Doux!</i></font>

298
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pawpaw!</font>

299
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for you, Pawpaw!</font>

300
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux made yours special and made 
your veggies into stars, Pawpaw.</font>

301
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you eat all the stars!</font>

302
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux!</font>

303
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made this just for me?</font>

304
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux!</font>

305
00:20:17,770 --> 00:20:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hopeless. I need to 
hurry and do something.</font>

306
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my. It's always so lively around Doux.</font>

307
00:20:25,410 --> 00:20:28,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lady Dahaka. This is no laughing matter.</font>

308
00:20:28,930 --> 00:20:31,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all happening because Lady 
Doux is spreading her kindness.</font>

309
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. But what do you think?</font>

310
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After seeing this, I'm fairly certain 
she'll be just fine tomorrow.</font>

311
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

312
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! So this is why you 
wanted us to go find Doux.</font>

313
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty?</font>

314
00:20:48,550 --> 00:20:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux, it was really yummy.</font>

315
00:20:51,610 --> 00:20:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the food!</font>

316
00:20:53,860 --> 00:20:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Bro, this is super tasty.</font>

317
00:20:56,620 --> 00:20:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it great that we 
came to this castle, Bro?</font>

318
00:20:59,690 --> 00:21:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's plenty more!</font>

319
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux!</font>

320
00:21:03,570 --> 00:21:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made a new magic potion!</font>

321
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

322
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

323
00:21:11,750 --> 00:21:14,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, amazing!</font>

324
00:21:14,330 --> 00:21:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry! 
I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry!</font>

325
00:21:17,220 --> 00:21:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it amazing?</font>

326
00:21:18,530 --> 00:21:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just learned this recently,</font>

327
00:21:21,100 --> 00:21:26,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but basically everyone who lives in 
the demon castle are Doux's friends.</font>

328
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Her friends?</font>

329
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demons and humans.</font>

330
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magical beasts and witches.</font>

331
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Possibly even others...</font>

332
00:21:38,150 --> 00:21:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone who's encountered Doux at 
least once mysteriously gather to her.</font>

333
00:21:45,150 --> 00:21:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why there's no need to worry.</font>

334
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux isn't scared of anything</font>

335
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so there's no need to force her to act 
a certain way or say certain things.</font>

336
00:21:55,660 --> 00:22:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as she's herself,
 she will look dignified to everyone.</font>

337
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, you're right.</font>

338
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is this really okay?</font>

